{% block title %}An Error Occurred: {{ status_text }}{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<h1>Sorry, something's gone wrong</h1>
<h2>The server returned a "{{ status_code }} {{ status_text }}".</h2>

<div>
    Something is broken. Please e-mail us at <a href="mailto:websupport@camdram.net">
